{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Content-Language","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Language","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>Content-Language</code></strong> 是一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Entity_header\">entity header</a>（实体消息首部），用来说明访问者希望采用的语言或语言组合，这样的话用户就可以根据自己偏好的语言来定制不同的内容。</p>\n<p>举个例子，假如设置了这样一条消息首部（ \"<code>Content-Language: de-DE</code>\" ），那么说明这份文件是为说德语的人提供的（当然这并不意味着文件本身就是用德语写的。比如，它可能是为说德语的人开设的英语教程的一部分，也就是用英语写的）。</p>\n<p>如果没有指明 <code>Content-Language</code>，那么默认地，文件内容是提供给所有语言的访问者使用的。多个语言标签也是合法的，同样的，这个首部还可以用来描述不同媒体类型的文件，而不单单局限于文本型文档。</p>\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Header type</th>\n      <th><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Entity_header\">Entity header</a></th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Forbidden_header_name\">Forbidden header name</a></td>\n      <td>no</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Simple_response_header\">CORS-safelisted response-header</a></td>\n      <td>yes</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Simple_header\">CORS-safelisted request-header</a></td>\n      <td>yes</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">Content-Language: de-DE\nContent-Language: en-US\nContent-Language: de-DE, en-CA\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"指令","title":"指令","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"language-tag\"><code>language-tag</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>多个语言标签需要用逗号隔开。每一个语言标签都是由一个或多个不区分大小写的子标签构成的，子标签之间用连字号 (\"-\", %x2D) 隔开。通常情况下，一个语言标签是由标识一个大的语言家族的主语言子标签（例如\"en\" = English），以及后面可选的用来缩小语言范围使更确切的一系列子标签（\"en-CA\" 表示在加拿大范围使用的英语的变种）构成的。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>备注：</strong> 语言标签在 <a href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc5646\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">RFC 5646</a>中被正式定义，它使用的<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Language_code\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">语言代码</a>依赖于 <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_639\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ISO 639</a> 标准 (通常为 <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_ISO_639-1_codes\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ISO 639-1 code list</a>) 。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"声明文档的书写语言","title":"声明文档的书写语言","isH3":true,"content":"<p>全局的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/lang\"><code>lang</code></a> 属性使用在 HTML 元素去表达全部的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML</a>文档或者部分的语言。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">lang</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>de<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>不要使用这个 meta 元素去声明文档语言：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html example-bad notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- /!\\ This is bad practice --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">http-equiv</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>content-language<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">content</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>de<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"为资源指定目标访问者","title":"为资源指定目标访问者","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>Content-Language</code> 请求头用于指定**页面的目标受众，**并且可以指明当前页面存在多种语言。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">Content-Language: de, en\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://httpwg.org/specs/rfc7231.html#header.content-language","title":"Hypertext Transfer Protocol (HTTP/1.1): Semantics and Content"}],"query":"http.headers.Content-Language"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"http.headers.Content-Language","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Language/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关内容","title":"相关内容","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Accept-Language\"><code>Accept-Language</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/International/questions/qa-http-and-lang.en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTTP headers, meta elements and language information</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"指令","id":"指令"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"相关内容","id":"相关内容"}],"summary":"Content-Language 是一个 entity header（实体消息首部），用来说明访问者希望采用的语言或语言组合，这样的话用户就可以根据自己偏好的语言来定制不同的内容。","popularity":0.0002,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Content-Language","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Content-Language","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Content-Language","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Content-Language","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Content-Language","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Content-Language","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/http/headers/content-language","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/http/headers/content-language/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP","title":"HTTP"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers","title":"HTTP Headers"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Language","title":"Content-Language"}],"pageTitle":"Content-Language - HTTP | MDN","noIndexing":false}}